OL,3,CCalls to address disabled parking
OL,4,Cconcerns
OL,6,FJersey's government has been
OL,7,Fcriticised for failing to deliver more
OL,8,Fparking spaces for disabled islanders.
OL,10,FFormer Deputy Jackie Hilton-Egre, who
OL,11,Fis also a Blue Badge holder, wrote to
OL,12,Fthe Infrastructure Minister Andy Jehan
OL,13,Fsaying she was "disappointed at the
OL,14,Flack of action".
OL,16,FAdditional spaces and other access
OL,17,Fconcerns had been discussed at a
OL,18,Fpublic meeting with Blue Badge holders
OL,19,Fin June.
