OL,3,CCalls to address disabled parking
OL,4,Cconcerns
OL,6,FThere are around 5,000 Blue Badge
OL,7,Fholders in Jersey although there are
OL,8,Fonly around 100 dedicated parking
OL,9,Fspaces.
OL,11,FDee Michoux, a Blue Badge holder, says
OL,12,Fshe normally avoids travelling into
OL,13,Ftown due to the lack of parking spaces
OL,14,Favailable.
OL,16,FShe explains: "With the town becoming
OL,17,Fa one-way system, it's not making it
OL,18,Fany easier for us disabled people
OL,19,Fanyway.
