OL,3,CCalls to address disabled parking
OL,4,Cconcerns
OL,6,F"We're pretty much second-class
OL,7,Fcitizens. They'll take the spaces from
OL,8,FBroad Street and put them into Harreck
OL,9,FStreet but realistically people have
OL,10,Fgot to walk further which is the issue
OL,11,Fin the first place."
OL,13,FIn response, Infrastructure Minister
OL,14,FAndy Jehan says he walked around St
OL,15,FHelier with Constable Simon Crowcroft
OL,16,Fin September and has now "identified a
OL,17,Fnumber of spaces we can convert to
OL,18,FBlue Badge holder".
