OL,3,CCalls to address disabled parking
OL,4,Cconcerns
OL,6,FIn writing, the figure was confirmed:
OL,7,F"16 new parking spaces in St Helier
OL,8,F... and we will also be trialing some
OL,9,Fnew road markings to make disabled
OL,10,Fbays more identifiable".
OL,12,FConstable Jehan also said he would
OL,13,Fsoon contact "all Blue Badge holders
OL,14,Fconfirming the locations" and that he
OL,15,Fwas "looking to establish a focus
OL,16,Fgroup to help us gather views".
